ddafi's words were unacceptable.\nGaddafi, who has a harem of young female bodyguards and a reputation for outlandish eccentricity, has been met with negative reactions from Muslims in Switzerland. \"In my opinion, this is a purely political matter between Libya and Switzerland, and has nothing to do with Islam or with Muslims,\" said the head of the mosque in Geneva. Yasar Ozdemir of the Swiss Federation of Muslim Associations said he was unsurprised by Gaddafi's \"nonsense.\""}
